oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: West Wood Drive-In Theaters... Assassin of Youth
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Motion picture theaters; Film posters; Motion Pictures;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (red and black on yellow) Hatch poster announcing the showing of "Assassin of Youth" plus two big featurettes "Million Dollar Legs" and "Nature Girl" at the West Wood Drive-in theater in Aberdeen, Mississippi on Tuesday, October 26 and Wednesday, October 27.
